== 評價 ==
此部電影得到廣泛好評，在知名網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]有高達97％的評價。影評與觀眾的評論多為：「聰明，優雅。託[[安東尼·霍普金斯|安東尼·霍普金斯]]和[[艾瑪·湯普遜|艾瑪·湯普遜]]無可挑剔的表演之福，此片成為了一部經典」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/remains_of_the_day/ |title=爛番茄評價 |accessdate=2014-05-05 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128114447/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/remains_of_the_day |dead-url=no }}</ref>。知名影評人[[羅傑·艾伯特|羅傑·艾伯特]]稱讚道：「一部體貼、細膩的電影」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-remains-of-the-day-1993 |title=The Remains Of The Day |accessdate=2014-05-05 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927125748/https://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/the-remains-of-the-day-1993 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》：「集合了[[安東尼·霍普金斯|安東尼·霍普金斯]]、[[艾瑪·湯普遜|艾瑪·湯普遜]]和[[詹姆斯·福斯|詹姆斯·福斯]]，就知道是一場精彩的演技表現」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/theremainsofthedaypghowe_a0b009.htm |title=The Remains of the Day |accessdate=2014-05-05 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927125753/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/theremainsofthedaypghowe_a0b009.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

